<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT5">
<l>irumpaṉaṉ ṟuṇṭa nīrpō lemperu māṉuk keṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>arumpeṟa laṉpu pukkiṭ ṭaṭimaipūṇ ṭuyntu pōṉēṉ</l>
<l>varumpuyal vaṇṇa ṉārai maruviyeṉ maṉattu vaittu</l>
<l>karumpiṉiṉ cāṟu pōlap parukiṉēṟ kiṉiya vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like water consumed by an iron burning, attaining once and for all</l>
<l>My love for our Lord, hard to acquire, and being bound [in his] service, I became saved,</l>
<l>Embracing him, the hue of the coming storms, and fixing my mind [on him];</l>
<l>Ah, the way that it is sweet to me who gulps [him] like sweet sugarcane juice!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
